# Finwiz Screener — project memory

- **Project name:** Finwiz Screener for Promising Growth Stocks
- **GitHub:** https://github.com/quantscout-nlp/finwiz-screener
- **Local root:** `D:\Finwiz Screener for Promising Growth Stocks`
- **Dashboard:** `.\launch_dashboard.ps1` → http://localhost:8501
- **CLI launcher:** `.\launch.ps1`

## Environment variables (never commit values)

| Purpose | Env var |
|---------|---------|
| Finviz Elite export | `FINVIZ_API_KEY` |
| OpenAI Query Lab | `OPENAI_API_KEY` or `FINWIZ_LLM_API_KEY` |
| Paper bot | Local ledger only — no API key required |

Never commit `.env`, API tokens, or secrets. Prefer User-level Windows env vars.

## Architecture reminders

- Finwiz = this local project; Finviz = data source (finviz.com / Elite)
- Core data: `data/tickers/*.json`, `data/index/search_index.json`, `config/toggles.json`
- Dashboard: Streamlit multi-page app in `dashboard/app.py`
- Elite sync: `scripts/sync_finviz_elite.py` / `scripts/finviz_elite.py`
